    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3095540/extras/e7330805c552534eaf193c7be7a035fe.poster.avif?t=1755089051\" width=360 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3095540/extras/e7330805c552534eaf193c7be7a035fe.webm?t=1755089051\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3095540/extras/e7330805c552534eaf193c7be7a035fe.mp4?t=1755089051\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏介绍：</h2>在《Choice Matters》中，你将扮演一位冒险者，踏上一段史诗级旅程。这是一款独特的资源管理卡牌游戏，每一个决定都将左右你的命运。穿越多重事件，合理管理资源，揭示每位角色背后的独特故事。你的选择能否带你走向胜利？还是会迷失方向并承受其后果？<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3095540/extras/43e5d57d16fd1ef0115508d20ae39f35.poster.avif?t=1755089051\" width=384 height=216 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3095540/extras/43e5d57d16fd1ef0115508d20ae39f35.webm?t=1755089051\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3095540/extras/43e5d57d16fd1ef0115508d20ae39f35.mp4?t=1755089051\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >核心特色：</h2><strong>决策驱动：</strong> 面对不同事件，做出关键抉择，改变你的旅程走向。<br><strong>资源管理：</strong> 谨慎分配资源，每个选择都会带来连锁反应。<br><strong>多样故事线：</strong> 扮演不同角色，每位角色拥有独立任务与剧情。<br><strong>Roguelike机制：</strong> 每次游玩都是全新体验，充满未知与机会。<br><strong>80+独特事件：</strong> 体验超过80种事件，挑战与奖励并存。<br><strong>30+遗物系统：</strong> 收集强大遗物，为冒险提供强有力支持。<br><strong>角色背景探索：</strong> 深入了解五位角色的过去与命运。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3095540/extras/904488a5a1cde662097d2c68bad4f47a.poster.avif?t=1755089051\" width=360 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3095540/extras/904488a5a1cde662097d2c68bad4f47a.webm?t=1755089051\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3095540/extras/904488a5a1cde662097d2c68bad4f47a.mp4?t=1755089051\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >重要提示：</h2>《Choice Matters》目前仍在开发中，我们将持续加入新的内容与挑战。如遇到任何问题，欢迎随时联系我们。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >关于 NUE GAMES：</h2><i>NUE GAMES 致力于打造沉浸式与创新性的游戏体验。《Choice Matters》为资源管理与构筑玩法带来全新视角，让选择与结果更具意义。</i><br>",
